  "texts": [
    "(a) Text Summarization is the process of condensing lengthy texts into manageable summaries that support content creation and information extraction (El-Kassas et al., 2021).",
    "Priya and Umamaheswari (2023) discusses how extractive summarization can be applied by generating summaries that focus on the most important parts of a text.",
    "This approach is particularly useful when dealing with large documents, as it allows for the extraction of key information while preserving the original meaning.",
    "(b) According to Pituxcoosuvarn and Ishida (2018), Machine",
    "Translation greatly enhances multilingual communication and information access by translating text from one language to another."
  ]
}